after drawing a glyph:
	let w0 w1 glyph displacement
	either t_x = ((w0 - T_j/1000)⋅T_{font_size}+T_c+T_w)⋅T_{horizontal_scaling}
	or t_y = ((w1 - T_j/1000)⋅T_{font_size}+T_c+T_w)
	then translate the text matrix.

